data.description: PRICE REDUCED / MOTIVATED SELLER!! $30k price reduction on this fantastic and immaculately kept Bill Clark home, on a corner lot and  built in 2017.The sellers are original owners and it still shows as brand new! This a must see in the highly desirable Arbor Creek community. A beautiful 3 bedroom/ 3 bath with a  master plus two guest bedrooms on the first floor,  and a wonderful Bonus Room over the garage with a full 3rd bath! A man cave? 4th bedroom? Game room? Endless options!An open family/dining/kitchen ''great room'' plus a wonderful sun porch and patio for grilling. Enjoy the fabulous amenities of Arbor Creek including the pool, the tennis courts, the clubhouse, the community garden...it just doesn't get any better!  Make this one yours!
